  "text": "We firstly evaluate several representative real-time semantic segmentation methods, including the simplified PSPNet [CITATION_1] , ICNet [CITATION_2] and our proposed method on the Cityscapes validation dataset. The simplified PSPNet is compressed with the kernel keeping rate of 0.5. ICNet is the recent promosing realtime semantic segmentation method. The comparison results are reported in Table VII .",
